<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>home</title>
  <style>
    /* ðŸŽ¨ Reset & Base */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1984ff, #96bcff);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #ffcc00;
    }

    /* ðŸ”¹ Nav */
    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      position: fixed;
      top: 1.5rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    /* âœ¨ Heading */
    h1 {
       margin-top: 3rem;
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6a00, #ee0979);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s ease;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 700px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* ðŸ”¹ Container for content card */
    .content-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      max-width: 800px;
      width: 100%;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease;
    }

    /* ðŸ”¹ Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }
      nav ul {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      .content-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    /* ðŸ”¹ Animations */
    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/">home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">about</a></li>
      <li><a href="/blog/new-blog">new blog</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <h1>Hello Again</h1>
  <div class="content-card">
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Omnis praesentium iste et quos eos laudantium odit possimus, id facere suscipit minima, tempora vero. Unde, assumenda perferendis a impedit accusantium consequuntur.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
